## Foreword </div>
I've made this book in an attempt to bring the beloved Warcraft franchise into the 5th Edition of Dungeons and Dragons. It is a task that has taken me months to do, and many more to come I am sure as I continue to work on this in my spare time.

My intention with this book have been from the start to make it as a free resource for all to use, and never to be bought or paid for, I do this because I want others to enjoy it, not because I want to earn money from it.

This books is made to compliment 5th Edition **Player's Handbook, Dungeon Master's Guide**, and **Monster Manual**. Using the rules presented in those and balanced around being playable in a standard D&D setting without requiring modifications.

All changes made in a new version of the handbook can be found by checking the link below. I've also provided a link to the races balancing document, in case someone likes numbers like me, Enjoy!

<div style="text-align:Center"> 

### [ChangeLog](https://drive.google.com/open?id=1AtTF7o6sAZZLxA75oa-96ENNNBMAJ-z7m9Y93uk4b8A)
### [Race Balance](https://drive.google.com/open?id=1S-XKXMaiLtRLpeIg9t50PvvAfEajpq72MxjTqa9ZbaI)
</div>

