| 13th|| +5 || 7d6 || Roguish Specialization feature                           |
| 14th|| +5 || 7d6 || Blindsense                                               |
| 15th|| +5 || 8d6 || Slippery Mind                                            |
| 16th|| +5 || 8d6 || Ability Score Improvement                                |
| 17th|| +6 || 9d6 || Roguish Specialization feature                           |
